{"word":"περιτρέχω","slug":"περιτρέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιτρέχω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-θρέξομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δρᾰμοῦμαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-έδρᾰμον</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-δεδράμηκα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to run round and round, run round</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to run about</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:— <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to be current, in vogue</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to run round</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to circumvent</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}